# Sports Arb Event Lifecycle

- For NBA/MLB monotonic arb scanning, resolved or past-date sports game markets should age out of the watchlist.
- Current/future NBA and MLB game slugs should be discovered automatically from Gamma instead of relying only on static env slugs.
- Do not keep trading or scanning a resolved sports game just because it remains in an env var.
